			<p><b><span style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;">Stage de théâtre enfants 8-12 ans sur le thème des contes.&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;"></b><br style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;"><span style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;">Par le biais d'exercices ludiques, mêlant théâtre et improvisation, les enfants aborderont un travail du corps, de la voix, apprendront à se positionner dans l'espace et à jouer ensemble.</span><br style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;"><br style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;"><span style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;">Ils construiront et interpréteront des personnages sur le thème des contes, qu'ils joueront dans le cadre de scénettes.</span><br style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;"><br style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;"><span style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;">Tous niveaux.</span><br style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;"><span style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;">Prévoir une tenue décontractée et un pique nique pour les repas du midi.</span><br style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;"><br style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;"><span style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;">Horaires : de 9h30 à 17h&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;"><span style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;">Intervenante : Maud Roussel</span><br style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.24px;"><span class="text_exposed_show" style="display: inline; font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(75, 79, 86); letter-spacing: -0.24px;"><br>Tarifs : 95€ non adhérent (comprend 10€ d'adhésion à l'association Le C.I.D.)<br>85€ adhérent<br><br>Infos et réservations auprès de 